226
00:24:14,620 --> 00:24:16,890
Áno.

227
00:24:23,810 --> 00:24:26,040
Áno!

228
00:24:33,310 --> 00:24:36,550
Eun Gi.

229
00:24:47,590 --> 00:24:50,090
