365
00:36:27,390 --> 00:36:28,190
Áno, Jae Gil.

366
00:36:28,190 --> 00:36:29,220
Kde si teraz?

367
00:36:29,220 --> 00:36:32,220
V našom dome je polícia, 
a všetko je hore nahami.

368
00:36:32,220 --> 00:36:33,890
Polícia?

369
00:36:34,290 --> 00:36:34,850
